元），是该集团在中国最大的单笔投资。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 04:03:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/ikea-shopping-mall-arm-opens-doors-1-bln-shanghai-development-2024-09-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国针对加拿大关税展开反歧视调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-launches-anti-discriminatory-probe-against-canadas-tariffs-2024-09-26/</link><description>中国商务部周四表示，中国对加拿大采取的限制性措施（包括对中国电动汽车、钢铁和铝产品加征关税）发起反歧视调查。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 03:46:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-launches-anti-discriminatory-probe-against-canadas-tariffs-2024-09-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国将向有需要的人提供一次性救济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-give-one-off-handouts-needy-2024-09-26/</link><description>一份政府声明称，中国将在下周国庆节前向弱势群体发放一次性补贴。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 03:17:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-give-one-off-handouts-needy-2024-09-26/</guid></item><item><title>据彭博社报道，中国考虑向顶级银行注资 1,420 亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-weighs-injecting-142-bln-capital-into-top-banks-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-26/</link><description>据彭博社周三报道，中国正在考虑向其最大的国有银行注入高达 1 万亿元人民币（合 1,423.9 亿美元）的资本，以增强其支持陷入困境的经济的能力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 03:04:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-weighs-injecting-142-bln-capital-into-top-banks-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-09-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国的经济刺激带动股市上涨，拉动亚洲股市走高；油瀑布</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-26/</link><description>周四，亚洲股市逆势而上，延续了中国主导的涨势，原因是人们对中国激进的经济刺激计划持持续乐观态度，而且有消息称可能会出台更多支持措施。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 02:29:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-26/</guid></item><item><title>台湾对来自“不稳定”中国的新军事威胁发出警报</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-surge-chinese-warplanes-off-its-coast-2024-09-26/</link><description>台湾国防部周四就台湾地区军事活动和实弹演习再度激增之际中国缺乏政策稳定性发出警告，称北京对其邻国构成了严峻挑战。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 02:18:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-surge-chinese-warplanes-off-its-coast-2024-09-26/</guid></item><item><title>美联储发言人关注美元大幅反弹后坚挺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firm-following-sharp-rebound-fed-speakers-eyed-2024-09-26/</link><description>美元在经历 6 月初以来的最大涨幅后周四保持坚挺，交易员期待当天晚些时候美联储主要政策制定者的讲话，以寻找有关降息步伐的线索。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 01:53:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firm-following-sharp-rebound-fed-speakers-eyed-2024-09-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示不会放弃争取乌克兰和平的努力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-says-it-will-not-give-up-efforts-strive-peace-ukraine-2024-09-26/</link><description>外交部长王毅在纽约会见欧盟高级官员博雷尔时表示，中方致力于缓和乌克兰局势，不会放弃争取和平的努力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 01:13:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-says-it-will-not-give-up-efforts-strive-peace-ukraine-2024-09-26/</guid></item><item><title>报纸报道日本驱逐舰首次通过台湾海峡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-destroyer-passes-through-taiwan-strait-first-time-newspaper-report-2024-09-25/</link><description>《读卖新闻》援引多名政府消息人士的话报道称，日本自卫队周三首次在台湾海峡巡逻，试图向中国传达信息。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 23:32:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-destroyer-passes-through-taiwan-strait-first-time-newspaper-report-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>香港法院判处两名前编辑在具有里程碑意义的案件中犯有煽动罪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-court-sentence-two-former-editors-found-guilty-sedition-landmark-case-2024-09-25/</link><description>香港一家法院将于周四对两名前编辑宣判，他们因发表有关中国香港国家安全镇压的文章而被判煽动叛乱罪，这一裁决引起了国际社会的强烈抗议。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 23:10:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-court-sentence-two-former-editors-found-guilty-sedition-landmark-case-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>日本首相候选人小泉谈到变革，但竞争对手可能会改变美国外交</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-pm-candidate-koizumi-talks-change-rivals-could-alter-us-diplomacy-2024-09-25/</link><description>在成为日本下一任领导人的竞争中，年轻的竞争者小泉进次郎将自己定位为变革候选人，但他的老对手石破茂和高市早苗则推动了可能在外交上动摇的政策。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 22:06:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-pm-candidate-koizumi-talks-change-rivals-could-alter-us-diplomacy-2024-09-25/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：随着中国刺激措施的消退，暂停在召唤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-25/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 21:50:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-25/</guid></item></channel></rss>